      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is looking for someone with a vision to bring it back to its former glory. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a restoration project or a valuable source for parts. Grab this diamond in the rough at a great price and make it your own!",
