    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is currently non-running. The engine requires a complete overhaul or replacement, and the transmission has significant slippage. Additionally, there is noticeable rust on the undercarriage and body panels, along with a worn interior that needs deep cleaning and repair. This is a project car best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts donor.",
