    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It will require extensive mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy again. The exterior has significant rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with several deep dents and peeling clear coat. Under the hood, the engine runs roughly and has a persistent oil leak, while the transmission shifts harshly. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. This is a project car for someone with the tools and time to invest in a total overhaul.",
      "price": 6500.0,
